---
title: Truffled Beef Tenderloin Ramen in a Pork Broth with Mushrooms, Bok Choy & Sesame Seeds
description: Indulge in a decadent bowl of ramen topped with juicy beef tenderloin and elevated with earthy truffle seasoning. Mushrooms, garlic, and scallions flavor a rich broth in which springy noodles and crisp bok choy and napa cabbage cook to perfection. Truffle butter adds more rich flavor, and a shower of nutty sesame seeds tops it all off!
